SOURCE: https://github.com/nightwatchjs/nightwatch-docs/blob/versions/3.0/docs/guide/writing-tests/using-test-hooks.md#2025-04-10_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = {
  beforeEach: function(browser, done) {
    // performing an async operation
    setTimeout(function() {
      // finished async duties
      done();
    }, 100);
  },

  afterEach: function(browser, done) {
    // performing an async operation
    setTimeout(function() {
      // finished async duties
      done();
    }, 200);
  }
};
```

